verbose_text: In the M2 --> GPe connection in control animals, we found that high-beta / gamma activity was attenuated by STR conditioning (16-37 Hz, P < 0.001); furthermore, we observed that 6-OHDA was associated with a significant suppression of activity in this band (27-37 Hz, P < 0.001 and 41-45 Hz, P = 0.004).
evidence: high-beta/gamma activity was attenuated by STR
